text: Bad location but insanely good Indian food. don’t go there in person, but it’s the best u can order from, it’s called Simplyy Indian on foodpanda

I've never been there eating. I always get delivery from them for the workers here. And I've changed my order items due to our workers are vegan.. and *Nila* has been patience enough to keep updating my orders. This is first class service.

Talk about food quality. I've ordered 18 - 30 packs in 1 shot but nothing changed and tasted just great pippin hot food served.

Delivery is on the dot. I need it for lunch they delivered on lunch time.

Side note for Nila, you've done a great job and your are still doing great. Keep it up!!

Every Monday the meat is not good .Suspect the previous old and recook meat they serve.
Got diarrhea and vomit after eating the lunch mutton curry and tandoori chicken.
Avoid meat on mondays
Best food in West area . Good service . Good quality restaurant food in food court
